    <!-- BOLTFLASHED PIECES -->
    <h2 class="section-heading">Boltflashed Pieces</h2>
    <div class="intro-row">
      <div class="portrait-area">
        <img alt="Boltflashed Pieces" src="https://catalog.jonsarkin.com/files/large/1571d1a647482295135fbb142e159c73d8ba17ff.jpg" />
      </div>
      <div class="intro-text">
        <p>For decades, Sarkin compulsively stuffed envelopes with drawings and mailed them unsolicited to strangers, critics, and public figures &mdash; a practice he called <em>boltflashing</em>. Known recipients include the New Yorker critic Calvin Tomkins (whose pieces are now in the MoMA Archives), the Eisner Award&ndash;winning cartoonist Tony Millionaire, and director Joel Schumacher. Many remain in unknown hands.</p>
        <a class="bio-link" href="https://catalog.jonsarkin.com/s/catalog/item-set/7491">View the catalog set &rarr;</a>
        <div class="boltflash-cta" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          <p>Did you receive unsolicited artwork from Jon Sarkin? <a href="&#109;&#97;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;&#58;&#97;&#114;&#116;&#64;&#106;&#111;&#110;&#115;&#97;&#114;&#107;&#105;&#110;&#46;&#99;&#111;&#109;">Contact the estate</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CURRENTLY AVAILABLE -->
    <h2 class="section-heading">Currently Available</h2>
    <div class="body-text">
      <p>A current selection from the estate. The full inventory is in <a href="/collections/all">Available Works</a>.</p>
    </div>

    {%- assign featured_handles_raw = section.settings.featured_handles | default: 'js-0000-10070,alphabet-series-complete-set-of-26-a-z,js-2017-8764' -%}
    {%- assign featured_handles = featured_handles_raw | split: ',' -%}
    <div class="product-grid product-grid--featured">
      {%- for handle in featured_handles -%}
        {%- assign handle_clean = handle | strip -%}
        {%- assign featured_product = all_products[handle_clean] -%}
        {%- if featured_product != blank and featured_product.handle != blank -%}
          <a href="{{ featured_product.url }}" class="product-card">
            <div class="product-card__image{% if featured_product.metafields.artwork.original_image_url %} product-card__image--hdr{% endif %}">
              {%- if featured_product.metafields.artwork.original_image_url -%}
                <img
                  class="product-card__img product-card__img--hdr"
                  src="{{ featured_product.metafields.artwork.original_image_url | replace: '/files/original/', '/files/medium/' | replace: '.jpeg', '.jpg' | replace: '.png', '.jpg' }}"
                  alt="{{ featured_product.title | escape }}"
                  loading="lazy"
                >
              {%- endif -%}
              {%- if featured_product.featured_image -%}
                <img
                  class="product-card__img product-card__img--shopify"
                  src="{{ featured_product.featured_image | image_url: width: 600 }}"
                  alt="{{ featured_product.title | escape }}"
                  loading="lazy"
                >
              {%- endif -%}
              {%- unless featured_product.available -%}
                <span class="product-card__sold-dot" aria-label="Acquired"></span>
              {%- endunless -%}
            </div>
            <div class="product-card__info">
              <div class="product-card__title">{{ featured_product.title }}</div>
              {%- if featured_product.metafields.artwork.medium -%}
                <div class="product-card__meta">{{ featured_product.metafields.artwork.medium }}{% if featured_product.metafields.artwork.support %} on {{ featured_product.metafields.artwork.support | downcase }}{% endif %}</div>
              {%- endif -%}
              {%- if featured_product.metafields.artwork.dimensions -%}
                <div class="product-card__meta">{{ featured_product.metafields.artwork.dimensions }}</div>
              {%- endif -%}
              <div class="product-card__price">
                {%- if featured_product.available -%}
                  {{ featured_product.price | money }}
                {%- else -%}
                  <span class="product-card__badge product-card__badge--sold">Acquired</span><span class="product-card__sold-price">{{ featured_product.price | money }}</span>
                {%- endif -%}
              </div>
            </div>
          </a>
        {%- endif -%}
      {%- endfor -%}
    </div>

